    <p style="margin-top:8px">Your intake form has been sent directly to your Will Power coach.<br>You'll hear from us shortly to confirm your programming session.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:24px;font-size:13px;color:var(--gray-500)">Didn't get a confirmation email? Check your spam folder or contact your coach directly.</p>
  </div>
